<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Farmer Login - FarmConnect</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #4CAF50;
            --secondary-color: #45a049;
            --accent-color: #2c3e50;
            --text-color: #333;
            --light-bg: #f8f9fa;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 900px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .quote-container {
            flex: 1;
            display: none;
        }

        @media (min-width: 992px) {
            .quote-container {
                display: block;
            }
        }

        .quote-box {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: white;
        }

        .quote-text {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .quote-author {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .card {
            flex: 1;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            color: var(--text-color);
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            padding: 40px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 450px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            animation: fadeInRight 0.8s;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .header-text {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: var(--accent-color);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .form-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--accent-color);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .form-control {
            border: 2px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 12px;
            padding-left: 40px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .form-control:focus {
            border-color: var(--primary-color);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.2rem rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.25);
        }

        .input-group {
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .input-group i {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            left: 15px;
            color: #6c757d;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .btn-submit {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-submit:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--secondary-color), var(--primary-color));
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.4);
        }

        .signin-link {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 25px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .signin-link a {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .signin-link a:hover {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
        }

        @keyframes fadeInRight {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInLeft {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(-20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container-wrapper">
        <div class="quote-container animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft">
            <div class="quote-box">
                <p class="quote-text">"The farmer has to be an optimist or he wouldn't still be a farmer."</p>
                <p class="quote-author">- Will Rogers</p>
            </div>
            <div class="quote-box">
                <p class="quote-text">"Agriculture is our wisest pursuit, because it will in the end contribute most to real wealth, good morals & happiness."</p>
                <p class="quote-author">- Thomas Jefferson</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card animate__animated animate__fadeInRight">
            <div class="header-text">
                <i class="fas fa-tractor mb-3" style="color: var(--primary-color); font-size: 2.5rem;"></i>
                <div>Farmer Login</div>
            </div>
            <form action="/loginFarmer" method="POST">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Enter your full name" required>
                </div>
                <div class="input-group">
                    <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
                    <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password" name="password" placeholder="Enter your password" required>
                </div>
                <div class="d-grid">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-submit">
                        <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt me-2"></i>Login
                    </button>
                </div>
            </form>
            <div class="signin-link">
                <p>Don't have an account? <a href="/signinFarmer">Sign Up</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
